inicio.phrase1: Ayoncotic ta jwohc’ yu’un tut smajanel taqu’in banti shachoj te jloqu’esej p’olmaliletic ta stojol bats’il swinquilel lum tseltal te ay ta jsehp squ’inalel yu’un Chiapas soc nix te ayoncotic ta yutil jwohc’ Yomol A’tel.
inicio.phrase2: Ha’ ini syomel sbah muc’ul slecubtesel a’telil ya jlehcotic xchahpanel yantic sbehlal stuqueltayel shachel a’tel soc pajal scoltayel jbahcotic ta smajanel taqu’in ta biluc wocolil te ya xc’oht ta pasel ta jlumalcotic.
inicio.phrase3: Ayotic ta spasel tulan ta sjeltayel sbehlal binut’il ta nopel yaqu’el te majan taqu’in soc nix tut smajanel taqu’in.
inicio.phrase4: Yacal jlehbelcotic muc’ yach’il sbehlal p’ijubtesel yu’un stuquinel taqu’in, ich’bil ta  muc’ spisil  bintic ay ta sjoylejal lum qu’inal soc te mach’atic tey ayic ah.
inicio.icon1: Uts stso’bil taqu’in soc bin ay cu’untic
inicio.icon2: Xcha’ yaqu’el ta a’tel slequilal ca’teltic
inicio.icon3: Cha’ox chahp xchahpanel yotsesel taqu’in soc wocoliletic
inicio.phrase5: Comon Sit Ca’teltic ha’ jun syuqu’el hach’el stomal a’tel, soc ya yich’ aqu’el ta juju xuht’ taqu’in banti ay to xan bin ya sc’an pasel.
inicio.phrase6: Yacal jlehbelcotic muc’ yach’il sbehlal p’ijubtesel yu’un stuquinel taqu’in, ich’bil ta  muc’ spisil  bintic ay ta sjoylejal lum qu’inal soc te mach’atic tey ayic ah.
inicio.phrase7: Jun halbil xchahpanel a’tel yu’un lec stuquinel taqu’in soc syomel jbahtic ta jun pajal.
conocenos.territorioP1: Ayotic ta sjsehp squinalel jlumaltic yu’un chiapas, te banti c’alal smacticlanej squ’inalel yu’un Chilon, Sitalá, Yajalon,Pantelhó soc Ocosingo. te squ’ixinal qu’inal ya spas yu’un ya yich’ ts’unticlanel capel ta yaxinal te’etic (ha’ shachi’bal a’telil te ya yotses talel jtaqu’intic ta yutil jnahtic), haxan te binti ya scoltayoncotic ta sjunal  jcuxlejalcotic ha’ te sit jts’unub cawalcotic te hay ta jujun jlum qu’inalcotic; te ixim, chenec’ soc bayel ta chahp sit tsu’nub awalil te ha’ ya xtuquin yu’un jwe’el cuch’elcotic soc lec stuquinel taqu’in ta scoltayel bahcotic ta yutil jnahcotic.
conocenos.territorioP2_1: Ta spisil te jsehp squ’inalel xcuxlejanilej stalel sc’ahyinel maya tseltal, banti ma’ ch’aybil te muc’ sc’oblal stalel sc’ahyinel jc’opojeltic, jtalel jc’ahyineltic soc yantic ta chahp a’telil ta comonal soc ya’teltayel sc’op cajwaltic. spisil ini, ta yomol soc te scanantayel jnantic lum qu’inal, banti  ya xhu’ cu’untic scanantayel te ya caltic
conocenos.territorioP2_3: (lequil cuxlejalil soc slamalil qu’inal) soc jcomonaltic, yutsilal qu’inal soc xch’uhunel co’tantic.
conocenos.territorioP3: Ha’nix hich, ha’ ini jsehp squ’inalel ha’ te c’ax me’ba obol hay ta jlumaltic Mexico. Manchuc nix ha’ jsehp qu’inal te nojel ta sc’uhlejal, haxan te yantic ants winiquetic ha’ ya sc’an ya yu’untaybeyic te sc’uhlejal bintic ay cu’uncotic ta jlum jqu’inalticotic.
conocenos.territorioP4: Ha’ yu’un la jnopcotic syomel jbahcotic yu’un ya xloc’oncotic ta ha’ ini coltayeletic yu’un taqu’in soc nix slehel hahchel yantic sbehlal cu’uncotic.
conocenos.yomolAtelP1_1: Yomol A’tel ya sc’an ya yal ta bats’il c’op tseltal
conocenos.yomolAtelP1_2: junax ya xha’tejotic, junax ya xbehenotic, junax ya xwayichinotic
conocenos.yomolAtelP1_3: . Ha’ jun jwohc’ syomoj sbah ta jujun muc’ul slecubtesel syomon bah chombajel soc smucu’btesel jwohc’ a’teliletic, hich binut’il te jwohc’ nahinel jloqu’esej p’olmalil ta squ’inalel jlumaltic yu’un chiapas soc nix te jwohc’ jcoltaywanej j’a’teletic te ayic ta stsahlalul squ’inalel spahmal lum Mexico.
conocenos.yomolAtelP2: Noc’ol ca’teltaybelcotic xchicnajtesel lec sbehlal syomel a’tel haxan ta jun pajal ya jlehbeycotic yantic sbehlal yu’un lec chahpambil stojol a’telil te yacal jloqu’esbelcotic ta jlum jqu’inalcotic ta yo’tic ini, ha’nix hich canantaybil ta spisil c’ahc’al te stsaquel sbah jol co’tantic soc te jnantic lum qu’inal haxan joquimbilotic yu’un te yantic jwohc’ jchahpanej a’telil te junax ay schaplejal jc’optic (Jwohc’ toyol nop hun, jwohc’ jcoltaywanejetic, jwohc’ yan jmohlola’btic te ya scoltayotic ta taqu’in, jwohc’ jman p’olmalil soc yantic jwohc’ p’ijubteseletic,soc yantic xan).
conocenos.cafeT: Jwohc canantaybil lec sbelal a’tel yu’un capel
conocenos.cafeP1: Sloqu’esel p’olmalil te lec chahpambil ta lequil swe’el lum qu’inal, sjelontesel ta pasel,schonel loq’uel p’olmalil ta yan lum te chahpambilix soc nix xchonel ta uch’ujibal.
conocenos.japonT: Jchahp bintic ya xtuhun cu’untic ta sbaxbultayel jbahtic ta tuhlutuhl
conocenos.japonP1: Chahpambil xapon, Sahqu’il Joltic, spoxil jwinquileltic soc luchiletic.
conocenos.microfinanczasP1: Tut smajanel taqu’in te ya yich’ tuquinel soc xchahpanel a’telil yu’un jwohl nahinel te ayic ta yutil Yomol A’tel.
conocenos.mielT: Jwohc canantaybil lec sbelal a’tel yu’un Cha’b
conocenos.mielP1: Sloqu’esel p’olmalil lec chahpambil ta lequil swe’el lum qu’inal soc chombajel ta yutil muc’ul lum méxico, ha’ te nopol nax sjelontesel ta pasel yu’un ya sohl bahel ta chahpambilix p’olmalil.
conocenos.comonP1: Comon Sit Ca’teltic hahch soc ya’teltayel jxuht’uc taqu’in banti chahpambil talel te slequilal a’tel yu'un stojol capel. tey a me ine la jlehbeycotic sbehlal ta tuquinel te taqu’in banti ya yich’ jachel yach’il a’tel yu’un ya xp’ohl xan mohel ah te shilemal sit a’telil soc hich yax a’tej xan ta yantic smuc’ubtesel sp’olel a’telil.
conocenos.comonP2: Ha’ ini jujun caj a’telilil yac’oj yo’tan ta ya’teltayel stuquinel taqu’in-smuc’ubtesel schahpanel a’telil banti xhu’ ya shach hachel sbah ta a’tel jwohl nahinel, ta jun comonal ma’uc teme ta jsehp squ’inalel.
conocenos.plataformaT: Schicnaji’bal smajanel taqu’in ta ac’bil xchicnaji’b
conocenos.plataformaP1: Binu’til yacal ta behenel bahel te schaplejal a’tel yacal ta muc’ubel hachel soc ya xtulanij hachel ta pasel, ha’nix hich ya xhu’ ya xhochotic ta bayuc jech c’alil ha’ yu’un hach ta a’beyel yich’ yip, soc laj yich chahpanel hachel ta a’teltayel ha’ ini jcaj a’telil.
conocenos.plataformaP2: comonsitcateltic.com ha’ banti chican spisil ta jay chahp a’teliletic soc ta yantic c’opojeletic  banti sjambeyejotic yach’il sbehlal a’tel cu’untic, soc ya xhu’ ya jna’beytic sbah yantic a’teliletic te binut’il chahpambil ay ta pasel ca’teltic c’alal ta yo’tic ini noc’ol jcholbeltic p’ijilal  soc ayotic ta slecubteselte ca’teltic.
conocenos.plataformaP3: Ya jna’tic te ha’ tulan sc’oblal yu’un ya jc’asestic ta a’iyel te binti jnopojtiquix, ha’ yu’un te mach’a hich yo’tan ya sc’an ya yil, sloc’tayel, soc scohtesel ma’uc teme slecubtesel binut’il chahpambil yahtalul, ya xhu’ ya ca pasic binut’il yaca c’anic,
conocenos.plataformaP5: Te chahpambil yahtalul xchicnahtesel a’tel jbehlaltesbil talel ta yomol soc te jcoltaywanej cu’untic ha’ te quichantic
mapa.title: Sloc'ombah jpahm qu'inal soc Bintic ay yu'un jsehp squ’inalel
mapa.p1: Ta yutil schahpanel jujun caj ini xchicnaji’bal a’telil ya jtahtic bayel ta chahp a’teliletic te ay ta yutil jsehp squ’inalel banti ya ca’beytic snop’ jpahm swinquilel lum
mapa.p2: Li’ ta yan uhetic baheli, ya scoltayotic te mach’atic yac’oj sbahic ta a’batinel soc stse’elil o’tanil ya jchahpantic jun sloc’ombah jpahm squ’inalel te jamal sbehlal yu’un ya xhochotic ta yilel bintic yacalic ta c’ohel ta pasel ta jpahm squ’inalel.
